{"title":"苹果和虫子2","uid":"ac05e299c896fafeaf879961438f88db","slug":"苹果和虫子","date":"2022-03-24T15:46:24.369Z","updated":"2022-03-24T15:46:24.369Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/苹果和虫子.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"苹果和虫子2\"><a href=\"#苹果和虫子2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"苹果和虫子2\"></a>苹果和虫子2</h2><h4 id=\"描述\"><a href=\"#描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"描述\"></a>描述</h4><p>你买了一箱n个苹果，很不幸的是买完时箱子里混进了一条虫子。虫子每x小时能吃掉一个苹果，假设虫子在吃完一个苹果之前不会吃另一个，那么经过y小时你还有多少个完整的苹果？</p>\n<h4 id=\"输入\"><a href=\"#输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入\"></a>输入</h4><p>输入仅一行，包括n，x和y（均为整数）。</p>\n<h4 id=\"输出\"><a href=\"#输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出\"></a>输出</h4><p>输出也仅一行，剩下的苹果个数。</p>\n<h4 id=\"样例输入\"><a href=\"#样例输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输入\"></a>样例输入</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">10  4  9</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"样例输出\"><a href=\"#样例输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输出\"></a>样例输出</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">7</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"思路\"><a href=\"#思路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"思路\"></a>思路</h4><p>见解答</p>\n<h4 id=\"解答\"><a href=\"#解答\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解答\"></a>解答</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\n#include &lt;cstdio&gt;\n#include &lt;math.h&gt;\n\nusing namespace std;\n\nint main()\n&#123;\n    int n, x, y;\n    cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; x &gt;&gt; y;\n    if (x &lt;&#x3D; y)&#123;\n    \tif (y % x &#x3D;&#x3D; 0)\n    \t\tif (y &#x2F; x &lt;&#x3D; n)\n    \t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; n - (y &#x2F; x) &lt;&lt; endl;\n    \t\telse cout &lt;&lt; 0 &lt;&lt; endl;\n    \telse \n\t\t\tif ((y &#x2F; x) + 1 &lt;&#x3D; n)\n\t\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; n - ((y &#x2F; x) + 1) &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\t\telse cout &lt;&lt; 0 &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t&#125;\n\telse if (x &gt; y &amp;&amp; y !&#x3D; 0)\n\t\tcout &lt;&lt; n - 1 &lt;&lt; endl;\n\telse cout &lt;&lt; n &lt;&lt; endl;\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n","feature":true,"text":"苹果和虫子2描述你买了一箱n个苹果，很不幸的是买完时箱子里混进了一条虫子。虫子每x小时能吃掉一个苹果，假设虫子在吃完一个苹果之前不会吃另一个，那么经过y小时你还有多少个完整的苹果？ 输入输入仅一行，包括n，x和y（均为整数）。 输出输出也仅一行，剩下的苹果个数。 样例输入10 4...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":813,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":12,"path":"api/categories/C.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":12,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"OpenJudge","slug":"OpenJudge","count":12,"path":"api/tags/OpenJudge.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%92%8C%E8%99%AB%E5%AD%902\"><span class=\"toc-text\">苹果和虫子2</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">描述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输出</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%B7%E4%BE%8B%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">样例输入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%B7%E4%BE%8B%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">样例输出</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">思路</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E7%AD%94\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解答</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"ARVIN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"求一元二次方程的根","uid"